<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Support Projexia - Donate</title>
    
    <!-- CSS Files -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/projexia-design-system.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar-modern.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer-modern.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/utility-pages-modern.css" />
    
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Poppins:wght@600;700&family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script src="/js/theme.js"></script>
    
    <style>
        .donate-container {
            max-width: 64rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }

        .donate-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .donate-header h1 {
            font-family: var(--font-poppins);
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
            color: hsl(var(--foreground));
        }

        .donate-header p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: hsl(var(--muted-foreground));
            max-width: 40rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .donate-content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .donate-content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .donate-header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }

        .donate-card {
            background: hsl(var(--card));
            border: 1px solid hsl(var(--border));
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .donate-card:hover {
            border-color: hsl(var(--primary));
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px hsl(var(--primary) / 0.15);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .donate-card h3 {
            font-family: var(--font-poppins);
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
            color: hsl(var(--foreground));
        }

        .donate-card p {
            color: hsl(var(--muted-foreground));
            margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .donate-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            background: hsl(var(--primary));
            color: hsl(var(--primary-foreground));
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            font-family: var(--font-inter);
        }

        .donate-button:hover {
            background: hsl(var(--primary) / 0.85);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px hsl(var(--primary) / 0.3);
        }

        .info-section {
            background: hsl(var(--primary) / 0.08);
            border: 1px solid hsl(var(--primary) / 0.2);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .info-section h2 {
            font-family: var(--font-poppins);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
            color: hsl(var(--foreground));
        }

        .info-section p {
            color: hsl(var(--muted-foreground));
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
        <!-- Navbar -->
        <%- include('partials/navbar-modern') %>
        
        <!-- Main Content -->
        <main style="flex: 1; padding-top: 4rem;">
            <div class="donate-container">
                <div class="donate-header">
                    <h1>Support Projexia</h1>
                    <p>Help us continue building the best platform for CCS students to showcase their projects and collaborate.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="donate-content">
                    <div class="donate-card">
                        <h3>Make a Donation</h3>
                        <p>Your support helps us maintain and improve Projexia for all CCS students. Every contribution makes a difference!</p>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: hsl(var(--primary));">Coming soon: Support us through donations via PayPal, GCash, or other payment methods.</p>
                        <button class="donate-button" disabled style="opacity: 0.6; cursor: not-allowed;">
                            Coming Soon
                        </button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="donate-card">
                        <h3>Partner With Us</h3>
                        <p>Interested in partnering with Projexia? We're always looking for sponsors and collaborators who share our vision.</p>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: hsl(var(--primary));">Get in touch with our team to discuss partnership opportunities.</p>
                        <a href="mailto:contact@projexia.dev" class="donate-button">Contact Us</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-section">
                    <h2>Why Support Projexia?</h2>
                    <p>Projexia is a student-built platform designed by CCS students, for CCS students. We're committed to creating a space where students can:</p>
                    <ul style="margin: 1rem 0 0 1.5rem; color: hsl(var(--muted-foreground));">
                        <li>Showcase their academic and personal projects</li>
                        <li>Discover and learn from other students' work</li>
                        <li>Build their professional portfolios</li>
                        <li>Collaborate and network with peers</li>
                        <li>Get recognition for their contributions</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">By supporting Projexia, you're investing in the future of our community and helping us create opportunities for students to grow and succeed.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <%- include('partials/footer-modern') %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
